{"tid":1470322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"面對五毛，連登仔可唔可以冷靜D，團結D","createTime":"2019-08-14T04:55:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T08:17:31.000Z","uid":3401,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b20699cece1a41d80b2c40883a01d279240bee8a","tid":1470322,"uid":3401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:55:28.000Z","msg":"琴晚成班五毛一出黎帶風向成班就亂哂<br />\n警察開槍無人提<br />\n警察逼供被捕人士唔提<br />\n之前發生既野又忘記哂<br />\n<br />\n一味覺得自己錯哂做乜鳩？<br />\n而家要做既係行返正個風向<br />\n<br />\n道歉岩唔岩我唔講<br />\n但如果純粹道歉就一定無用<br />\n只會比人覺得我地無啦啦打人<br />\n<br />\n要比人知道當晚發生左咩事你先道歉架大佬<br />\n有大陸警察同香港警察入侵示威活動帶頭搞破壞阿！<br />\n<br />\n中共係遙言高手大家都知，但大家又準備好打言論戰未呢？"},{"pid":"e7e8c4f02247dad81057f388980f954b3606b407","tid":1470322,"uid":3401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:55:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ba835627cad1acb7bedb24079fb5a0f0fc58554","tid":1470322,"uid":3401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:57:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"47cc3dfc5cb8c336ea0c7e9a312f4652f9398ce0","tid":1470322,"uid":3401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:00:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"517bb180607828610e514c084253a8bedebcf539","tid":1470322,"uid":3401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:05:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4943d2d4e42165e88ec165513b88eeda638a8f90","tid":1470322,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:05:42.000Z","msg":"我地應該每星期搵一日，同一個時間一齊搭車入機場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468945</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b51f280c7eea4e1f4bd02414c4c67fb0670727ad","tid":1470322,"uid":55775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:06:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4fa827b0e9c71f134ea1db432cbe0c5588a3aad3","tid":1470322,"uid":3401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:35:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6